data.description: This lovely 4 bedroom 3/bath home is located in the most sought after community of Colony Preserve.  This is an ALL AGE community full of wonderful neighbors.  The Clubhouse is a 2 second walk that has great amenities for the kids; basketball, swimming pool and a wonderful tot lot.  Minutes to downtown Delray, the beach and all airports.  Swim in privacy in your own in-ground pool that backs up to a Preserve.  Modern kitchen with snack bar and eat-in cafe area.   Lots of sliding glass doors that bring in the natural light throughout the home. Wonderful guest quarters on the main level with their own bath.  Three bedrooms up including a wonderful bonus office/nursery off the master.  You have found your dream home.....
